strings: <voice_0x01001378><se_def>Black and white: Does the angry dog fly east?
<voice_0x01001379><se_def>Black and white: Head east, my lord... I think Padre Island is to the east.
<voice_0x0100137A><se_def>Black and white: Tall They chased the little dog! to not give up
<voice_0x0100137B><se_def>Black and white: We cannot allow another human life like our mother to be sacrificed. Can you find and win them?
<voice_0x0100137C><se_low>King of tricks: Believe me, you don't even have to put him on the criminal list to convince us.
<voice_0x0100137D><se_low>King of tricks: But now let's do something! Hey, we have finally caught the devil in Paris! Do you really want to continue?
<voice_0x0100137E><se_def>Black and white: .. that's the answer! delicious!
<voice_0x0100137F><se_def>Black and white: If the enemy can fly, they should be able to fly with the help of Kutenjindori!
<voice_0x01001380><se_def>Black and white: Each ruined temple has its own monument.
<voice_0x01001381><se_def>Black and white: Explains how to fight crime.
<voice_0x01001382><se_def>Black and white: If anyone could help him in this battle, the kingdom would surely help him.
